# Pre-Research — Orschell Excavating E-Commerce Full-Stack

Answers to the 5 planner research questions, plus additional findings.

---

## Q1: Orschell's actual business

Services-only excavating company (septic systems, ponds, driveways/road building, land clearing/forestry mulching, demolition, building pads). They do NOT sell excavation equipment or parts. They currently operate a **branded merchandise store at orschellx.com** (apparel + accessories). The e-commerce posting is most plausibly to build a proper backend for their existing/planned merch store, or a planned supply store expansion.

**Implication for demo**: Frame "Orschell Supply Co." as their merch + construction supply store. Hero products = their actual branded apparel; supporting categories = realistic supply expansions (safety gear, site supplies). This is truthful AND demonstrates a full feature set.

---

