## Q3: Visual/design direction — confirmed and refined

orschellx.com confirms: **dark background, black/grey/neon orange** — their product colorways are "flow orange/black" and grey. Brand phrases: "Dirt Hammers", "Keep Banging Em" — rugged working-class identity.

**Refined palette** (adjust planner's draft):
| Token | Proposed | Refined | Note |
|---|---|---|---|
| Accent primary | `#F5A623` (amber) | `#F76B10` (construction orange) | Matches their actual "flow orange" brand |
| Accent hi-vis | `#FFD600` (caution yellow) | `#FFD600` | Keep — valid safety color |
| All other tokens | (as planned) | unchanged | Steel background palette confirmed correct |

Typography (Barlow Condensed + Inter) — confirmed correct for industrial/construction aesthetic.

