- decisions: demo = "Orschell Supply Co." merch + supplies store (matches real orschellx.com business); construction orange (#F76B10) over amber; node:sqlite not better-sqlite3; adverteyes auth/route middleware is directly reusable
- next needs: planner integrates product seed data (20 products above), corrects accent to #F76B10, removes "TBD" placeholders, adds testing approach section to plan
- risks: node:sqlite built-in requires Node 22+ — confirm Surface is Node 22 before build (it is per CLAUDE.md); adverteyes db.ts seed pattern uses better-sqlite3 pragma calls — verify node:sqlite supports same pragma syntax (it does)
